questions.explanation:
&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;The logic followed here is;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Logic:&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt; Difference of the top numbers&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 4&amp;nbsp;= Bottom Number.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Now, checking the figures:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage65afcdfabfaa61afb28ff92d.png&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; (6 - 2)&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;times; 4&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 4&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 4 = 16.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage65afcdfbbfaa61afb28ff949.png&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rarr; (5&amp;nbsp;- 4)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;times; 4&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 1&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 4 = 4.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage65afcdfbbfaa61afb28ff959.png&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rarr; (7&amp;nbsp;- 2)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;times; 4&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 5&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 4 = 20.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage65afcdfbbfaa61afb28ff95b.png&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rarr; (5&amp;nbsp;- 3)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;times; 4&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 2&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 4 = 8.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage65afcdfcbfaa61afb28ff95d.png&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rarr; (8&amp;nbsp;- 5)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;times; 4&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 3&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 4 = 12.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;Option 4&amp;quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;यहाँ अनुसरण किया गया तर्क यह है;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;तर्क: &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;शीर्ष संख्याओं का अंतर &amp;times; 4 = निचली संख्या&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;अब, आंकड़ों की जाँच:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage65afcdfabfaa61afb28ff92d.png&quot; /&gt;&amp;rarr; (6 - 2) &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;times; 4 &amp;rarr; 4 &amp;times; 4 = 16.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage65afcdfbbfaa61afb28ff949.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rarr; (5 - 4)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;times; 4 &amp;rarr; 1 &amp;times; 4 = 4.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage65afcdfbbfaa61afb28ff959.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rarr; (7 - 2)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;times; 4 &amp;rarr; 5 &amp;times; 4 = 20.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage65afcdfbbfaa61afb28ff95b.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rarr; (5 - 3)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;times; 4 &amp;rarr; 2 &amp;times; 4 = 8.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage65afcdfcbfaa61afb28ff95d.png&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rarr; (8 - 5)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;times; 4 &amp;rarr; 3 &amp;times; 4 = 12.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: var(--bs-body-font-family); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);&quot;&gt;अतः, सही उत्तर &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: var(--bs-body-font-family); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align); font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;विकल्प 4&amp;quot; है।&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
